                    "stepText": "Using the effective growth rate you identified for the first scenario, set up the expression for the dangerous amplitude $!$A_{danger}$!$ reached in $!$10\\,\\text{minutes}$!$. Select the expression that correctly represents $!$A_{danger}$!$.",
